machine_end_gcode:
M104 S0 ;extruder heater off
M140 S0 ;turn off bed
G91 ; relative positioning
G1 E-1 F300 ;retract the filament a bit before lifting the nozzle, to release some of the pressure
G1 Z+0.5 E-5 F600 ; move Z up a bit and retract filament even more
G90 ; absolute positioning
G28 X20 Y20 ;move X/Y to min endstops, so the head is out of the way
M84 ;steppers off
machine_start_gcode:
G90 ; absolute positioning
M140 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single] ; set bed temp and continue
; Nozzle warmup before home to avoid driving hardened ooze into glass
HOLD_TEMPERATURE MIN=160; wait for no-ooze warmup hotend temp
G28 ; home all axes

;G1 Z50 F3000 ; raise the nozzle for final warmup and clean
M109 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] ; set hotend temp
M190 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single] ; wait for bed temp

;G91 ; relative positioning
;G1 E-1 F300 ; retract to avoid ooze
;M117 10s pause for nozzle clean
;G4 P10000 ; dwell for 10s
;M117 ; clear message
;G90 ; absolute positioning

G1 X0.0 Y0.0 Z0.2 F300 ; set nozzle to 0.2
G92 E0.0 ; reset extruder distance position
G1 X60.0 E9.0 F1000.0 ; intro line
G1 X100.0 E21.5 F1000.0 ; intro line
G0 Z2

G92 E0.0 ; reset extruder distance position
name: MPU_D6 0.4 nozzle
